          },
          "displayName": "Li Lu",
          "active": true,
          "timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
        },
        "body": "Hi [~zjshen], do you think this will affect the data schema design of aggregation storages as well, or it's an \"entity table only\" change? I think this is independent to the aggregation implementations but would like to double check it. Thanks! ",
        "updateAuthor": {
          "self": "https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=gtcarrera9",
          "name": "gtcarrera9",
          "key": "gtcarrera9",
          "avatarUrls": {
